Hello <%= @wrapup.owner.display_name %>,

Another month has passed.  Give your collaborators some love and encourage them to come back by sending a monthly status email.  The email could include:

- What they've accomplished this month
- What you'll be using the transcribed material for
- Call to action - "Know anyone else who would be interested in working on this collection?  Invite them to join in on the fun."
- Here's an article with more help on writing a monthly newsletter:

<%= link_to "http://content.fromthepage.com/crowdsourcing-project-newsletter", 'http://content.fromthepage.com/crowdsourcing-project-newsletter', target: '_blank', rel: 'nofollow' %>

Here are the statistics for all of your collections in the past month:

- <%= number_with_delimiter @wrapup.work_count %> Total <%='Work'.pluralize(@wrapup.work_count) %>
- <%= number_with_delimiter @wrapup.completed_work_count %> Completed <%='Work'.pluralize(@wrapup.completed_work_count) %>
- <%= number_with_delimiter @wrapup.page_count %> <%='Page'.pluralize(@wrapup.page_count) %>
- <%= number_with_delimiter @wrapup.contributor_count %> <%='Contributor'.pluralize(@wrapup.contributor_count) %>
- <%= number_with_delimiter @wrapup.transcription_count %> <%='Page'.pluralize(@wrapup.transcription_count) %> Transcribed
- <%= number_with_delimiter @wrapup.edit_count %> <%='Page'.pluralize(@wrapup.edit_count) %> Edited
<% if @wrapup.translations? %>
- <%= number_with_delimiter @wrapup.translation_count %> <%='Page'.pluralize(@wrapup.translation_count) %> Translated
<% end %>
<% if @wrapup.ocr_corrections? %>
- <%= number_with_delimiter @wrapup.ocr_count %> OCR <%='Correction'.pluralize(@wrapup.ocr_count) %>
<% end %>
<% if @wrapup.subjects_enabled? %>
- <%= number_with_delimiter @wrapup.subject_count %> <%='Subject'.pluralize(@wrapup.subject_count) %>
- <%= number_with_delimiter @wrapup.mention_count %> <%='Reference'.pluralize(@wrapup.mention_count) %>
- <%= number_with_delimiter @wrapup.index_count %> <%='Page'.pluralize(@wrapup.index_count) %> Indexed
<% end %>

Here are the email addresses of all collaborators (for all time) on your collections:

<%= @wrapup.contributor_emails %>

You can see your overall statistics in the <%= link_to "Summary tab", summary_url(@wrapup.owner), target: '_blank', rel: 'nofollow' %> of your owner dashboard.  You can see each collection's statistics on the collection collaborator tab.

Sincerely,
The FromThePage Team
